    - French
    - Greek
 * Update to jlibtorrent 1.2.0.6

Version 1.2 (2016-11-30)
========================

 * Bugfixing
 * Added:
    - Torrent sorting
    - Dark theme
    - Ability to use random port
    - Forced encryption
    - Ability to add a torrent without starting
    - Redirect HTTP link support
 * Added new translations:
    - Chinese
    - Spanish
    - Polish
 * Update to jlibtorrent 1.2.0.4

